import sys

def main():
    x = float(sys.stdin.readline())
    a = int(x)
    b = int(round((x-a)*10))

    print(a, b)

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()

from math import floor, ceil

x = float(input())

f = floor(x)
c = ceil(x)

if c - x < x - f:
    print(c, f)
else:
    print(f, c)

def main():
    n = float(input())
    n = n % 1
    n = n * 100

    a = int(n / 10)
    b = int(n % 10)

    print(a, b)
